post.description:
Filter a GeoJSON to only include geometries fully contained within city boundaries.

This endpoint accepts a GeoJSON FeatureCollection and returns a filtered version
containing only features whose geometries are completely within the city boundaries.

Args:
    city_identifier: City identifier (e.g., 'bari_41038')
    geojson_data: GeoJSON FeatureCollection to filter (in request body)
    source: Data source for boundaries - 'cloud' (default) or 'local'
    bucket_name: GCS bucket name (only used when source='cloud')

Returns:
    GeoJSON FeatureCollection with filtered features (only geometries fully contained within boundaries)

Example Request:
    POST /cities/bari_41038/filter-geojson?source=cloud
    Body: {
        "type": "FeatureCollection",
        "features": [
            {
                "type": "Feature",
                "geometry": {
                    "type": "Point",
                    "coordinates": [16.87, 41.12]
                },
                "properties": {...}
            }
        ]
    }
